**Summary:**  
CXL’s article is excellent on clarity, copywriting, and practical testing advice, but to compete at the very top and cover all customer decision points, it must deepen its conceptual foundations (jobs to be done), include structured design frameworks (Value Proposition Canvas), link to broader strategy/business fit considerations, and expand on emotional/social customer insights and competitive analysis tools. Implementing these prioritized actions will align CXL with “the standard” and help close the content gap effectively.